channel.title: I cant log into my character!please help!
channel.description:
ok so i try to log into my account on a server. everything is ready all the info, etc. i click to log in and it shows loading on the top left corner and on my command prompt it says Exception in thread "Thread-4" java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space at RSString.method1612(RSString.java:856) at Class21.method336(Class21.java:188) at Class21.method350(Class21.java:520) at Class61.method598(Class61.java:337) at client.method33(client.java:767) at Applet_Sub1.method30(Applet_Sub1.java:558) at Applet_Sub1.run(Applet_Sub1.java:156) at java.lang.Thread.run(Unknown Source)
i try to log in on another account and it works!! if anybody can help me it will be very nice!!!!!!!!!! thanks.
